    "The <b>Wall of Flesh</b> is the final and strongest <linked>pre-Hardmode</linked> <linked>boss</linked>, spawnable only in <linked>The Underworld</linked>. Once it is defeated, the world permanently converts to <linked>Hardmode</linked>, which brings new content and challenges.",
